entry.title: Release of bitcoin-s 1.9.1
entry.summary: Bitcoin-s, a set of bitcoin libraries written in Scala, has released version 1.9.1. The project adheres to the Discreet Log Contract specification and for more information on it, users can visit bitcoin-s.org or read the release notes for the new version. The libraries are available on GitHub at https://github.com/bitcoin-s/bitcoin-s/releases/tag/1.9.1.
